## 4. Key Files & Entry Points

### Entrypoints
- `src/index.ts` - CronJob: poll → analyze → notify
- `src/serve.ts` - Dashboard: Express server on port 8080

### Core Logic
- `src/poller.ts` - Fetches launches and failed test items from ReportPortal
- `src/analyzer.ts` - Groups by version/tier, computes health, identifies new failures
- `src/config.ts` - All configuration from environment variables

### Data Layer
- `src/db/schema.ts` - SQLite schema (launches, test_items, acknowledgments, triage_log)
- `src/db/store.ts` - Queries and CRUD operations

### External Integrations
- `src/clients/reportportal.ts` - ReportPortal API (launches, test items, logs, defects, analysis)
- `src/clients/jira.ts` - Jira API (search, create, link issues)
- `src/notifiers/slack.ts` - Slack Block Kit message builder
- `src/notifiers/email.ts` - HTML email digest builder

### API Routes
- `src/api/routes/` - Express routes for dashboard operations

### Frontend
- `src/dashboard/public/` - Vanilla JS SPA with status matrix, triage, trends, flaky tests

